                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Savh.<add>?</add></placeName>\n                                        <date>25 Nov. 1850</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>My dear Sir,</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I return you the letter<lb/> of the Ed. of the\n                                        Jewish Chronicle, with my<lb/> answer. and which you may <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">Copy</hi> and<lb/> send him, or\n                                        you may inform him that I<lb/> decline any controversy with\n                                        him, the more<lb/> especially as I never see his paper, and\n                                        as<lb/> I have neither time, nor inclination for the<lb/>\n                                        work. I would not publish his letter, nor<lb/> my replyâ€”but\n                                        if you publish one, then<lb/> lets both go in together.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(9)\">In haste yrs truly &amp; <sic>sincerly</sic></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">Solomon Cohen</hi>\n                                        </persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd. I. Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>"
                  },
